Brought son #4 in after baseball practice. It was his first experience.  He was blown away that you could put as many toppings on the pizza for the same price.  So what does he order?  Pepperoni.  Too funny.  I got a Jasper with - chicken, pepp, hamburger, spicy sausage, feta, kalamata olives, cilantro, mushrooms, sun dried tomatoes, asiago and basil.  All on their fantastic gluten free crust.  Delicious!!!  Friendly staff.... clean restaurant.